text: Sabina Luciani (born 18 June 1963) is a Danish taekwondo athlete. She competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, where taekwondo was a demonstration sport, in the welterweight event. At the 1988 European Taekwondo Championships she won the bronze medal in the -65 kg category. == References == Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Martial artists
